(559, 'Bachelor of Psychological Science and Business', 'Bachelor of Psychological Science and Business', 'Monash University Malaysia. Established in 1998, Monash University Malaysia is the third largest campus of Australia\'s largest university and the first foreign university campus in Malaysia. We are a premier research-intensive Australian university ranked among the top 50 universities globally by the Times Higher Education World University Rankings 2023, and a member of Australia’s prestigious Group of Eight (Go8). Monash University is also ranked 42 in the latest QS World University Rankings.\r\nA self-accrediting university, our campus offers a distinctly international and culturally rich environment with approximately 9300 students from more than 79 countries. Students are taught by highly qualified academic staff from across the world and the same rigorous standards are applied at the campus as at other Monash campuses.', 6, 1, 108, '4500 RM per year', '4 years', 'Minimum CGPA of 2.5,IELTS:5.5', '36000 RM per year', '450 RMB', 'February, July, October.', 'https://admin.edumatric.com/uploads/coursedocument/LlPsPznhNxKLTNWGLRj8qhcV53lDezAi9yFYAy9V.jpg', '2023-09-26 18:00:00', '2023-09-26 18:00:00', '2023-09-27 01:56:23', '2023-09-27 01:56:23'),
